Program Author: Shakil Muhammad (101259661)

Purpose: Encrypt a string of plain text with a user-set key according to a predetermined set of rules
and decrypt encoded messages with the correct key

Headers: <stdio.h>, <string.h>
Source code: a2-Shakil.c

Compilation Command: gcc -Wall -o a2 a2-Shakil.c

Launching instructions: 
    Start program using: ./a2
    Select function (encrypt or decrypt), initalize preffered key and input plain text or an encoded 
    message
